  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "二分答案求中位数",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>原问题</strong>：谁是中位数？",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "\\to <strong>二分转化</strong>：中位数是不是 $\\ge X$ ？",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "根据中位数的定义：<strong>如果一个数组的中位数</strong> $\\ge X$，<strong>那么这个数组里至少有一半的数字</strong> $\\ge X$。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "这时候，数字瞬间只剩下两类：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$\\ge X$ 的数：统统标记为 <strong>1</strong>。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "$< X$ 的数：统统标记为 <strong>-1</strong>（或者 0）。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>于是，一道复杂的 “求中位数” 题目，变成了一道 “求和” 题目：</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "> 只要这个 0/1 数组的和大于 0（即 1 的数量多于 -1），那么中位数就一定 $\\ge X$。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "对顶堆求中位数",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "struct TwoSet {\n\t// priority_queue 比 multiset 更快\n\tpriority_queue<int> l;\n\tpriority_queue<int, vector<int>, greater<int>> r;\n\tint len = 0;\n\tvoid insert(int x) {\n\t\tlen++;\n\t\tif (l.empty() or x <= l.top())l.push(x);\n\t\telse r.push(x);\n\t\tint mid = (len + 1) / 2;\n\t\twhile (l.size() > mid) {\n\t\t\tr.push(l.top());\n\t\t\tl.pop();\n\t\t}\n\t\twhile (l.size() < mid) {\n\t\t\tl.push(r.top());\n\t\t\tr.pop();\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tint get() {\n\t\tif (len == 0)return -1;\n\t\treturn l.top();\n\t}\n};",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
